track_notes: Why not make a day of it? This is a FB walk taking you via the Coll de Ses Fontanelles, a good place for a drink in the shade of some small trees. I made a day of it and met a group of walkers from our club who arrived on the summit after our activation. They came up via a shorter route. I took over then as leader and we came back the same way as we went up.
track_title: From free car park near to Si Illot Bar

track_notes:
Go early, parking quickly gets full, GPS pos: 39.873234, 3.170612
Long (and boring) gravel road at first, followed by a steeper mountain track.
Lots of mountain goats on the summit!
track_title: From parking at Ermita de la Victoria
